{"tid":2371072,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[牛扒師] M9西冷、肉眼開箱","createTime":"2021-01-18T13:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T13:47:03.000Z","uid":260581,"like":44,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1c16b6530ab1c4a15333073525f404ac19c93315","tid":2371072,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4edFx0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4edFx0d.jpg&h=7ebf391e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8Fkx0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8Fkx0d.jpg&h=7f586e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0srtyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0srtyz.jpg&h=b6cd2570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早幾日見到做緊65折，所以我就買黎試下<br />\n西冷睇落靚過肉眼好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲買左包芝士漢堡春卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VhyS1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VhyS1e.jpg&h=6a998385&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcQXAeA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcQXAeA.jpg&h=c7fa4d7c&s={SIZE}\" />春卷我拎去氣炸，有少少重口味<br />\n但都惹味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWuaaNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWuaaNC.jpg&h=ed5f9510&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1cbEFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1cbEFY.jpg&h=813240c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PfPmhsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfPmhsE.jpg&h=11fb8ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76R0x0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76R0x0Z.jpg&h=cb5a0d61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qb0x00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qb0x00.jpg&h=5ea610e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛扒今次我冇reverse sear,就咁煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煎完扒個油再拎黎煎蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛扒、飯同蛋就夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7342b37e2b6627e869679618d925658cffc7056","tid":2371072,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddd3740cbda8f825ba3ca62dc2869759fe22af3","tid":2371072,"uid":41368,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"咁靚嘅扒整碟頭飯"},{"pid":"f11bc2d131e9c9011b6b94da697f682f8116a826","tid":2371072,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dfbfce2b186023daf0a14bf4fbb660d1de2cd2","tid":2371072,"uid":30635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b4e0412f91218ff794591ff7169389a0354a7e","tid":2371072,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"氣炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj